                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">コストゼロ</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">初期3,000円のみ、月額無料</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">5分で完了</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">AI名刺撮影でVCard変換</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">4言語対応</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">日英中西で国際ビジネス支援</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">フォロー率40%</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">AIと多言語効果で向上</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Cost Comparison Chart -->
    <div class="mt-16 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-8">コスト比較</h3>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Traditional Business Cards -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">従来の紙名刺</h4>
          <div class="bg-red-50 rounded-lg p-6">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-2">¥3,000</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">年間300枚</div>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <div>印刷費: ¥3,000</div>
              <div>整理時間: 30分</div>
              <div>環境負荷: 高</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- TapForge -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">TapForge</h4>
          <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-lg p-6">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">¥3,000</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">初期費用のみ</div>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <div>月額料金: ¥0</div>
              <div>整理時間: 5分</div>
              <div>環境負荷: ゼロ</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center mt-6">
        <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-600">
          海外案件を増やしたいフリーランサーに最適
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
